<section>
	<h3>Form follows function</h3>
	<p>Let's give our page a clean <a href="/helloworld/modernist/">modernist style</a>.</p>
	<ol>
		<li>Create a new file named <code>modernist_style.css</code>. This is called a stylesheet.</li>
		<li>
			<p>Link your stylesheet to your HTML file by adding a <code>link</code> tag.</p>
			<p>Between the opening and closing <code>head</code> tags, add this:</p>
			<pre><code>&lt;link rel=&quot;stylesheet&quot; href=&quot;modernist_style.css&quot;&gt;</code></pre>
		</li>
	</ol>
	<p>Control spacing using <code>margin</code> and <code>padding</code>.</p>
	<p>Control typography using <code>color</code>, <code>font-family</code>, <code>font-size</code>, <code>font-weight</code>, and <code>line-height</code>.</p>
	<p>Control decoration using <code>background</code> and <code>border</code>.</p>

</section>
